      Classes in au.edu.anu.rscs.aot.queries.base that implement Queryable 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      class  AndQuery
      Query testing if all its sub-queries are satisfied.
      class  CountQuery
      Checks that an integer ('count') is within a range.
      class  IsQuery
      Checks that an object is a Query.
      class  NotQuery
      Query testing if all its sub-queries are not satisfied.
      class  OrQuery
      Query testing if at least one its sub-queries is satisfied.
      class  SelectQuery
      A query to select items based on multiplicities.
      class  SequenceQuery
      Chains a sequence of queries, i.e. the result() of each query serves as an input into submit(...) of the next query.
      class  SizeQuery
      Query testing if the size of a Sizeable object is within a specified range.
      class  XorQuery
      Query testing if exactly one its sub-queries is satisfied.
